      <title>大厂动效落地</title>
      <link href="/2020/09/07/%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%82%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0/"/>
      <url>/2020/09/07/%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%82%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>常见的有 Loading 动画、卡牌抽取动画、徽章展示动画等等。动画有简单的、有复杂的、有时间短的、有时间长的、有特效的，导致我们的落地方案呈现多样化。上面所述的动画我们把它归类为<span class='p green'>直接落地输出可见动画</span></p><div class="note blue"><p><strong>间接落地交互动画：引导用户交互、页面转场、提高用户体验等</strong></br> 这种动画的输出是不需要很多软件和插件来配合的，只需要给开发提供一份动效输出文档，文档内容需要包括：标注动效前后静态设计稿，口头描述或可以演示的 MP4，并且需要给到开发具体动效参数。（例：用户点击后购物车按钮尺寸 100%-50%，旋转 0°-180°，X 轴位 50px，Y 轴位移 20px，动效持续 400ms）</p></div><p><img src="https://img.zcool.cn/community/015cb25f4dd4ff11013f1a644e5982.gif" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://img.zcool.cn/community/015cb25f4dd4ff11013f1a644e5982.gif" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="img1"></p><h2 id="几种常用的输出方案"><a href="#几种常用的输出方案" class="headerlink" title="几种常用的输出方案"></a>几种常用的输出方案</h2><p class='p black'>1、设计师又爱又恨的 GIF</p><p class='p black'>2、流畅稳定有损的视频</p><p class='p black'>3、一般都会用到的精灵图</p><p class='p black'>4、适合多特效的 APNG/WEBP</p><p class='p black'>5、近几年流行的落地格式 LOTTLE/SVGA</p><h3 id="①-GIF"><a href="#①-GIF" class="headerlink" title="① GIF"></a>① GIF</h3><div class="note"><p>GIF的全称是Graphics Interchange Format，可译为图形交换格式，实现和开发成本低的有损格式，仅支持8位256色但具有很强的兼容性 </br> <code>体积大，质量差，尤其是透明的动画一定要慎用。</code></p></div><div class="timeline"><!-- 节点1 --><div class="timenode"><div class="meta"><p><ol><li>PS+视频输出</li></ol></p></div><div class="body"><p>1.1 通过 AE 导出视频格式（AVI 视频）后，再通过 PS 导出 GIF<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img2.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img2.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>1.2 将视频拖进 PS 后，导出 GIF 操作如下“文件 —— 导出 —— 存储 Web 所用格式旧版 —— 存储完成”这样输出的质量偏差、体积一般。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img3.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img3.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img4.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img4.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p></div></div><!-- 节点2 --><div class="timenode"><div class="meta"><p><ol start="2"><li>PS + 序列图</li></ol></p></div><div class="body"><p>2.1 通过 AE 导出 PNG 序列图后，再通过 PS 导出 GIF<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-5.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-5.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>2.2 序列图文件夹拖进 PS 方法（文件 —— 打开 —— 选择第一张图 —— 必须勾选图像顺序 —— 打开）<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img6.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img6.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>2.3 导出操作方法和视频用 PS 导出 GIF 方法一样，这样输出的质量一般、体积一般。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">注意：PS到处是GIF有时会失败，可能原因:</span><br><span class="line">1. 动画时间过长</span><br><span class="line">2. 图像尺寸太大</span><br><span class="line">3. FPS的数量限制（FPS就是每秒有多少帧）</span><br><span class="line">4. 莫名其妙的失败</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div><!-- 节点3 --><div class="timenode"><div class="meta"><p><ol start="3"><li>AE插件GIFFUN直接导出</li></ol></p></div><div class="body"><p>自行搜索插件-安装-导出<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img8.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img8.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p></div></div><!-- 节点4 --><div class="timenode"><div class="meta"><p><ol start="4"><li>视频</li></ol></p></div><div class="body"><p><code>实现成本低，兼容性强，能够直接播放视频、音频的有损文件，体积一般。一般用在宣传、开屏、演示如抖音、快手的开屏动画。讲下 MP4 的输出和压缩方案</code></br><br>4.1 将视频拖入 PS，然后通过 PS 导出 MP4<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img9.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img9.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>4.2 AE 导出视频的方法：AE —— 合成 ——添加到渲染队列 —— 选择 Quicktime —— 选择输出路径 ——确定<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img10.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao-img10.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao11.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao11.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br>1.3 将视频拖入 PS 后导出 MP4 的方法：PS —— 文件 ——导出 —— 渲染视频 —— 命好名字 —— 选择文件夹（输出到哪）—— 品质高中低（品质越高内存越大）—— 渲染<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao13.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao13.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao14.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tzblog/cloud@master/wenzhang/dongxiao14.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p><code>压缩视频的方案有——Handbrake、格式工厂、Adobe Media Encode。使handbrake无需特别技巧便可直接将DVD电影内转换成AVI/MPEG4格式,还有MP4及OGM输出、AAC 及 Vorbis 编码</code></p></div></div></div><p style="color: green; text-align: center" >未完待续，剩下的更精彩哦~</p><details green><summary> <p>版权声明：该文章来自<a href="https://www.zcool.com.cn/article/ZMTE3MzgyOA==.html">是北瓜呀（站酷）</a>如有冒犯，请留言，致歉侵删，谢谢！</p> </summary>              <div class='content'>                            </div>            </details>]]></content>
      
      
